       other domain-specific error codes.

       EEBBAADDFF  Bad descriptor.

       EEFFAAUULLTT The   socket  structure  address  is  outside  your
              address space.

       EENNOOTTSSOOCCKK
              The descriptor is not associated with file which is
              not a socket.

       EEIISSCCOONNNN
              The socket is already connected.

       EECCOONNNNRREEFFUUSSEEDD
              Connection refused at server.

       EETTIIMMEEDDOOUUTT
              Timeout while attempting connection.

       EENNEETTUUNNRREEAACCHH
              Network is unreachable.



